{"tid":2308720,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"用乜壞乜叫春區：一齊分享代理維修經歷","createTime":"2020-12-02T05:48:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T09:47:12.000Z","uid":267965,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"57bfea18f40e5f3e9651af7870669414ede9d5a8","tid":2308720,"uid":267965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T05:48:10.000Z","msg":"唔知呢兩個禮拜係咪得罪電腦之神，屋企D電腦野輪住壞，俾大家睇下條list<br />\n<br />\n底板：ASUS TUF B450M PRO GAMING （2020年2月買）<br />\nNAS：Synology DS920+ （2020年11月買，全新都可以壞）<br />\nMONITOR：Gigabyte G32QC （2020年3月買）<br />\n原本想買RTX 3070，依家都唔敢買住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，等D野整返好先再算<br />\n我好想玩Cyberpunk 2077<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但個mon係聯強代理維修，聽講聯強代理出名閪，唔知佢要整幾耐，喊出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n順便拋磚分享一下係代理維修嘅經歷。<br />\n<br />\n漢科：整ASUS底板，間野係觀塘，一個禮拜內可以拎到翻新板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，營業時間去到18：30<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nACW：整Synology NAS，間野係北角，維修佢會幫你RMA寄去台灣（唔使錢），要2-3個禮拜時間維修，營業時間去到18：00，因為未整完，之後再update<br />\n<br />\n聯強：整Gigabyte Mon，打完電話俾客服佢話會有師傅上門拎Mon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，因為今日先打電話，之後再update。"},{"pid":"4f579f36d089d744a536919f073b974e5592716c","tid":2308720,"uid":209890,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T05:52:25.000Z","msg":"MSI AG32比隻貓整爆左<br />\n之後去換MSI AG32CQ<br />\n特價2599$ 第一日拎MON<br />\n番到屋企裝完 右下角爆MON裂左<br />\n立即CALL代理換<br />\n查過我開機時間係0 (一小時以上就無得攪)<br />\n代理EMAIL左去問依加未知結果<br />\n不過應該好大機會有得換掛<br />\n右邊黑鳩左 個MON花左好多唔清 好似得360P咁<br />\n曲MON真係好撚化學<br />\n好似輕力摸下都會爆咁樣"},{"pid":"c1a8dfca2ecc2d3a38b7e26f97183dbd9f7f020a","tid":2308720,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T06:05:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />華石板<br />\n技尻BYE MON<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}